quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,48,"Okhurula khale benya okhubarerera obutswanzwani, mana nibakhukalukhanilia amakhuwa okhula shingala obulamba bwetsa, ne likhuwa lia Nyasaye niliba habulafu nabo nibalachamile tawe."
  9,49,"Ne mubo balimwo baboolanga mbu; “Mbe obwiyangu, ne olandema tawe.” Lola! Toto abo bamala okhukwa mumatemo. Ne toto Jahannam iliterera Abakhayi."
  9,50,"Obulayi nibukhunyoola, nibubasinyisia. Ne amasila nikakhunyoola, nibaboola mbu; “Khwahenga obulayi amakhuwa kefu okhurula khale (okhukhaya okhunyoolwa namasila)", ne bakalukhananga nibabwao nibasangalile."
  9,51,"Boola mbu; “Sishitsa okhunyoola shiosishiosi tawe habula shilia shia Nyasaye yakhuhandichila. Ye ni Omwami wefu.” Kho, abasuubili besiche Nyasaye butswa."
  9,52,"Boola mbu; “Enywe shimulindilanga efwe shiosishiosi tawe halali okhunyoola shilala khubulayi bubili. Ne efwe khulindanga Nyasaye abasandie nende eshinyasio okhurula khuye nohomba okhurulana nende emikhono chiefu. Kho, linde butswa, fwesi khuliindanga ninanyu.""
  9,53,"Boola mbu; “Rusie emiandu chienyu nimuchamile nohomba nimulachamile, shichilafuchililwa okhurula khwinywe tawe. Toto enywe muli Abandu barumanga amalako.’’"
  9,54,"Ne sishiabekalila okhuchamilwa eshihanwa shiabu halali mbu khulwa bakhaya Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe. Ne shibetsanga okhulama tawe halali nibali abatofu, ne shibahininjia eshihanwa tawe halali nibalachamile ta."